{"title":"种子与土地","authors":["肖韶光"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子与土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖韶光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群最早觉醒的播种者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把自己作种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与十月真理的种子嫁接"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探索在中国土地上发芽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有满腔热血滋润着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将理想与信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同一个阶级的利益"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打造镰刀斧头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣言开天辟地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种子不在土地中萌动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在土地中窒息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族深层扎根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史底蕴生发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破土出摧枯拉朽的生机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔节成华夏脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为新中国奠基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片根据地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以土地改革赢得土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把民主富强之根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍植九百六十万平方公里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的稻穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簇拥和辉煌出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国至高无上的神圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那位大地巨子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾饱蘸井冈星火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延河波涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用简朴形象的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥笔写来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震古烁今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦只要不脱离土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有永立不败的根基"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}